description._content: Description: 23. Pine plantation established on former blowing sand dunes similar to those shown in 20,21,22 above. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: 24. Sand dune, similar to that shown in 21 above, successfully arrested and fixed by acacia plantation. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives. Feel free to share it within the spirit of the Commons Please use the comments section below the pictures to share any information you have about the people, places or events shown.
